H0.text: Which British Prime Minister served the constituencies of Limehouse and Walthamstow West. Ramsay MacDonald

H1.text: Which British Prime Minister served the constituencies of Limehouse and Walthamstow West. Herbert Morrison

H2.text: Which British Prime Minister served the constituencies of Limehouse and Walthamstow West. George Lansbury

H3.text: Which British Prime Minister served the constituencies of Limehouse and Walthamstow West. Attlee

A4.text: At the 1922 general election, Attlee became the Member of Parliament (MP) for the constituency of Limehouse in Stepney.

A5.text: He lived to see his old constituency of Walthamstow West fall to the Conservatives in a by-election in September 1967.
